    nmap <buffer> <Leader><C-m> :<C-u>let loc_item = line('.') <bar> call qf#switch(2, 0, 0) <bar> exec loc_item.'ll'<CR>

    " nmap <buffer> <C-w>p <Plug>(qf_loc_switch) " location lists in pairs..
